192
00:09:07,298 --> 00:09:09,092
¡Ser valorado!

193
00:09:09,675 --> 00:09:13,054
<i>¡Tan valorado que nadie me abandonará</i>
<i>y todos me cuidarán!</i>

194
00:09:13,137 --> 00:09:14,472
QUIERO SER VALORADO

195
00:09:15,014 --> 00:09:17,475
